import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import { Breadcrumb, BreadcrumbItem, Button, Label, Col, Row, } from "reactstrap"; import { Control, Form, Errors } from "react-redux-form"; import { Link, withRouter } from "react-router-dom"; import { connect } from "react-redux"; import { postFeedback } from "../redux/actionCreators"; const required = (val) => val && val.length; const maxLength = (len) => (val) => !(val) || (val.length <= len); const minLength = (len) => (val) => (val) && (val.length >= len); const isNumber = (val) => !isNaN(Number(val)); const validEmail = (val) => /^[A-Z0-9a-z._%+-]+@[A-Z0-9.-]+\.[A-Z]{2,4}$/i.test(val); const mapDispatchToProps = (dispatch) => ({ postFeedback: (id, firstname, lastname, telnum, email, agree,contactType,message) => dispatch(postFeedback(id, firstname, lastname, telnum, email, agree,contactType,message)) }); const ContactComponent = (props) => { function handelSubmit(values) { console.log(values); var randomId= Math.floor(Math.random()*(100 - 0)) + 0; var formRandomId = "formId-"+randomId; props.postFeedback(formRandomId, values.firstname, values.lastname, values.telnum, values.email, values.agree, values.contactType, values.message) props.resetFeedbackForm(); } const errormsg = { firstnameError: "", lastnameError: "", }; var msg = ""; return (
